ISLAMABAD, May 29 (APP):Minister for Foreign Affairs Bilawal Bhutto Zardari has congratulated Recep Tayyip Erdogan on winning re-election as President of Turkiye.
In a tweet on soical media platform Twitter, he said, “Heartiest congratulations to Recep Tayyip Erdogan on his re-election. His historic victory reflects the trust of the Turkish nation in his visionary leadership. Wishing Türkiye eternal peace and prosperity as we continue our unique journey of brotherhood.”
